<h4><a href="https://www.buzzfeed.com/natashajokic1/vma-2020-winners">Lady Gaga 成 2020 MTV VMA 颁奖典礼大赢家</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1362407" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sub-buzz-5696-1598836833-1.jpg" alt="" width="700" height="415" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sub-buzz-5696-1598836833-1.jpg 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/sub-buzz-5696-1598836833-1-360x213.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
